Finally TheMrXshow had enough, so he made a video holding a [[dildo]] to his [[Gunt|crotch]] as if it was his penis. He claimed it proved he had a penis. The video was laughed at and the conclusion was drawn that he really didn't have a penis and the [[dildo]] was his [[Prosthetic_Penis|prosthetic penis]]. TheMrXshow removed his [[dildo]] video in less than 12 hours after uploading it.  
