==Sexual Assualt Threats==
TheMrXshow fell under attack after he was exposed for mass subscribing to underage kids with his numerous sock accounts. He had also been talking and flirting with the kids for extended periods of time. He thought he could hide his subscriptions at some of his accounts unaware that there was still a way to view them while at other accounts he left them right out in the open. All of his sock accounts were well know because when somebody blocked him at one account he would just come back in another saying the same shit until they had blocked all of his accounts. A number of videos were made filming the convos and the accounts of the kids to expose what he was doing, as a result TheMrXshow removed the comments box from most of his sock accounts. 
<br>
After being exposed as a [[Pedophile|child jockey]] his world began to crumble. One night he was asked to come to [[blogtv]] to talk live to the sexy young [http://www.youtube.com/user/ItalianBrawd ItalianBrawd] little did he know this was a set up and the convo would be filmed/recorded. ItalianBrawd let loose with a barrage of insults calling TheMrXshow a [[pedophile]]. TheMrXshow went [[batshit insane]] and began screaming threats of sexual assault. The [[lulz]] of the event are still being enjoyed today.
